<meta charset="UTF-8" />
<meta content="UTA Edenred. Your specialist for mobility solutions." name="description"/>
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1" />
<meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge">
<title>UTA - Subscription</title>
<link rel="stylesheet" href="{ basePath }/assets/styles/styles.css?{ versionKey }" />
<link rel="stylesheet" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/icon?family=Material+Icons">
<!-- webruntime-branding-shared stylesheets -->
<link rel="stylesheet" href="{ basePath }/assets/styles/salesforce-lightning-design-system.min.css?{ versionKey }" />
<link rel="stylesheet" href="{ basePath }/assets/styles/dxp-site-spacing-styling-hooks.min.css?{ versionKey }" />
<link rel="stylesheet" href="{ basePath }/assets/styles/dxp-styling-hooks.min.css?{ versionKey }" />
<link rel="stylesheet" href="{ basePath }/assets/styles/dxp-slds-extensions.min.css?{ versionKey }" />
<!-- webruntime-branding-shared stylesheets -->
<link rel="icon" type="image/png" href="{ basePath }/sfsites/c/resource/res_poc2/favicon.png">
<link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/select2@4.1.0-rc.0/dist/css/select2.min.css" rel="stylesheet" />
<link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/flag-icon-css/0.8.2/css/flag-icon.min.css">
<style>
   @font-face { font-family: 'Edenred';
   src: url('{ basePath }/sfsites/c/resource/res_poc2/fonts/edenred_regular.woff2') format('woff2'); }
   @font-face { font-family: 'Edenred'; font-weight: 700;
   src: url('{ basePath }/sfsites/c/resource/res_poc2/fonts/edenred_bold.woff2') format('woff2');}
   @font-face { font-family: 'Ubuntu';
   src: url('{ basePath }/sfsites/c/resource/res_poc2/fonts/ubuntu_regular.woff2') format('woff2');}
   @font-face { font-family: 'Ubuntu'; font-weight: 700;
   src: url('{ basePath }/sfsites/c/resource/res_poc2/fonts/ubuntu_bold.woff2') format('woff2');}
   @font-face { font-family: 'Ubuntu'; font-weight: 500;
   src: url('{ basePath }/sfsites/c/resource/res_poc2/fonts/ubuntu_medium.woff2') format('woff2');}
    
   header {
   		height: 0px !important;
   }
   body * {
       -webkit-box-sizing: border-box;
       box-sizing: border-box;
       text-decoration: none;
       font-family: Ubuntu, sans-serif;
       /*font-weight: normal;*/
       font-style: normal;
   }
   main, footer {
   		outline: rgb(255, 255, 255) 0px solid !important;
   }    
    .bold {
       font-weight: bold !important;
    }
    main {
  min-height: calc(100% - 195px);
}
    .flagicon {
  width: 25px !important;
    }
   .slds-input {
       height: 40px;
       display: -webkit-box;
       display: -ms-flexbox;
       display: flex;
       -webkit-box-align: center;
       -ms-flex-align: center;
       align-items: center;
       -webkit-box-pack: start;
       -ms-flex-pack: start;
       justify-content: flex-start;
       padding: 0 15px;
       border-radius: 4px;
       border: 1px solid #dedede;
       width: 100%;
       outline: none;
       -webkit-transition: 0.2s all cubic-bezier(0.17, 0.67, 0.83, 0.67);
       transition: 0.2s all cubic-bezier(0.17, 0.67, 0.83, 0.67);
   }
   .slds-input:focus, slds-input:active, slds-input:hover {
   		border: 1px solid #666;
   }
   .slds-input:focus {
       -webkit-box-shadow: 0 0.2rem 0.4rem rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.075) !important;
       box-shadow: 0 0.2rem 0.4rem rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.075) !important;
   }
   .section-content.community_layout-section_section { padding: 0px !important; }
   .community_layout-section_section-host  { padding: 0px !important; }
   .columns-content.community_layout-section_section { max-width : 100%!important; }
    
   :root {
       --ost--titlepage--color: rgb(51 62 77);
       --ost--titlepage--size: 1.75rem;
       --ost--titlepage--lineheight: 2.25rem;
       --ost--subtitle--color: rgb(51 62 77);
       --ost--subtitle--size: 1.25rem;
       --ost--subtitle--lineheight: 1.75rem;
       --ost--subtitle--weight: 500;
       --ost--subtitle--marginbottom: .5em;
       --ost--txt--color: rgb(92 111 138);
       --ost--txt--size: 1em;
       --ost--txt--lineheight: 1.5rem;
       --ost--fldlbl--color: rgb(51 62 77);
       --ost--fldlbl--size: .875em;
       --ost--fldlbl--lineheight: 1.125rem;
       --ost--infoblue--bullebackground: rgb(19 131 192);
       --ost--infoblue--color: rgb(92 111 138);
       --ost--fldlblbold--color: rgb(51 62 77);
       --ost--fldlblbold--size: 1em;
       --ost--fldlblbold--lineheight: 1.5rem;
       --ost--fldlblbold--weight: 700;
   }
   .osttitlepage {
       margin-bottom: 24px;
       font-family: Edenred, sans-serif;
       color: var(--ost--titlepage--color);
       font-size: var(--ost--titlepage--size);
       line-height: var(--ost--titlepage--lineheight);	
   }
   .ostsubtitle {
       color: var(--ost--subtitle--color);
       font-size: var(--ost--subtitle--size);
       line-height: var(--ost--subtitle--lineheight);	
       font-weight: var(--ost--subtitle--weight);
       margin-bottom: var(--ost--subtitle--marginbottom);
   }
   .osttxt {
       color: var(--ost--txt--color);
       font-size: var(--ost--txt--size);
       line-height: var(--ost--txt--lineheight);	
   }
   .ostfldlbl {
       color: var(--ost--fldlbl--color);
       font-size: var(--ost--fldlbl--size);
       line-height: var(--ost--fldlbl--lineheight);	
   }
   .ostinfoblue {
       color: var(--ost--infoblue--color);
       background-color: var(--ost--infoblue--bullebackground);
   }
   .ostfldlblbold {
       color: var(--ost--fldlblbold--color);
       font-size: var(--ost--fldlblbold--size);
       line-height: var(--ost--fldlblbold--lineheight);	
       font-weight: var(--ost--fldlblbold--weight);	
   }  
   .ostfldradio {
       color: black;
       font-size: var(--ost--fldlblbold--size);
       font-weight: 500;	
   }
   .ostheadimg {
       margin-right: 2rem;
   	   width: 3rem;
       height: 3rem;
   }
   .ostroundcomment
   {
       position: relative;
       top: -2px;
       box-sizing: border-box;
       display: inline-flex;
       align-items: center;
       justify-content: center;
       height: 16px;
       width: 16px;
       border-radius: 16px;
       background-color: black;
       color: white;
       font-size: .5rem;
       margin-right: 6px;
       margin-left: 6px;
   }
   .ostroundcomment:hover .tooltiptext {
        visibility: visible;
   }
   .ostroundcomment .tooltiptext {
       visibility: hidden;
       top: -80px;
       width: 200px;
       background-color: black;
       color: #fff;
       padding: 5px 0;
       border-radius: 6px;
       position: absolute;
       z-index: 1;
       line-height: 1.2rem;
       padding: 16px;
       font-size: 12px;
   }
    
      @media screen and (max-width: 1000px) {      
      .osttitlepage {
        margin-bottom: 40px;
      }
      .ostheadimg {
        display: none;
      }
    }
</style>
